Variation toolkit
Author:
	Pierre Lindenbaum PhD
	plindenbaum@yahoo.fr
Motivation:
	tool handling VCF, FASTA, bio* files.
WWW:
	http://code.google.com/p/variationtoolkit/
Documentation:
	The documentation is available as a TeX file in doc/varkit.tex

Compilation:
	before compiling, edit the file config.mk and
	change the path to samtools, tabix, etc...
	edit the file config.mk as described in the documentation
	
	Type:
		make clean
		make all doc
		make install
